data.description: Price Reduced! This one story gem offers the perfect blend of modern upgrades and comfortable living. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a plethora of desirable features.  The open kitchen has custom stone work throughout with ample counter space. Custom live edge wood burning fireplace is the heart of the living room with panoramic water views of the Strait.  The large family room includes its own bathroom, mudroom, office and seperate entrance to the home.  Fully fenced, private backyard  for entertaining. Lots of parking with a long driveway and 2-car detached garage provides ample storage for all your toys.  Recent upgrades include: updated bathrooms, upgraded flooring, upgraded fixtures and much more.Easy downtown access and VIEWS.
